article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

Partial cloudiness early, with scattered showers and thunderstorms during the afternoon. High around 60F. Winds ENE at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 50%..

Tonight

A widely scattered shower or thunderstorm is possible this evening. Then cloudy skies overnight. Low 42F. Winds N at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 30%.

og.description: CHEYENNE – With another legislative session just around the corner, the perennial calls for the state to expand Medicaid to about 20,000 low-income adults have begun anew.
og.title: Proponents argue for Medicaid expansion
